Definition.WordDefinition:
Elsewhere \Else"where`\, adv. 1. In any other place; as, these trees are not to be found elsewhere. [1913 Webster]
2. In some other place; in other places, indefinitely; as, it is reported in town and elsewhere. [1913 Webster]
elsewhere adv : in or to another place; "he went elsewhere"; "look elsewhere for the answer"
